whole PDFs (PRODUCTION_COMPLETION_BLUEPRINT.md §4.5 Stage A; Checkpoint 3). Prepared 2026-07-11.

Sources:
- `docs/source/Final SOP - Loan Disbursement V10 (1).pdf` — cited below as **V10 p.N** (33 pages;
